name: Casecreation
tagline: This is a python project that creates a particular 2-Dimensional test case of a cancer patient with tumors and OARs
body:
This project creates a circular body 2-D test case to be used to try algorithms in Radiation Therapy
I anticipate this will be used to test the efficiency of beamlet size discretization and aperture controled tomotherapy
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
